(5, 23, 'InvestorKYC', '{\"title\":\"Investor KYC\",\"introduction\":\"Dear Shareholders, This is to inform you all that SEBI via Circular No. SEBI/HO/MIRSD/MIRSD _RTAMB/P/CIR/2021/655 dated November 3, 2021 has mandates to listed companies to record PAN, Nomination, KYC details and Bank details of all shareholders.\",\"circularInfo\":\"The said circular can be access through link -\",\"circularLink\":\"https://www.sebi.gov.in/legal/circulars/nov-2021/common-and-simplified-norms-for-processing-investor-s-service-request-by-rtas-and-norms-for-furnishing-pan-kyc-details-and-nomination_53787.html\",\"formsTitle\":\"Forms to be filed with Company / RTA :\",\"forms\":[{\"name\":\"ISR  1\",\"link\":\"/UploadedFiles/Files/Form%20ISR%20-1%20-%20Form%20for%20availing%20investor%20services%20KYC.PDF\",\"description\":\"Form for availing investor services/KYC\"},{\"name\":\"ISR  2\",\"link\":\"/UploadedFiles/Files/Form%20ISR%20-2%20-%20Signature%20Verification%20from%20Bank.pdf\",\"description\":\"Signature Verification from Bank\"},{\"name\":\"ISR  3\",\"link\":\"/UploadedFiles/Files/Form%20ISR%20-3%20%20-%20Opting-out%20from%20Nomination.pdf\",\"description\":\"Opting-out from Nomination\"},{\"name\":\"ISR  5\",\"link\":\"/UploadedFiles/Files/1.%20Investor%20Complaints_31.12.2022.pdf\",\"description\":\"Request for Transmission of Securities by Nominee or Legal Heir\"},{\"name\":\"SH 13\",\"link\":\"/UploadedFiles/Files/Form%20SH-13%20-%20Nomination%20Form.pdf\",\"description\":\"Nomination Form\"},{\"name\":\"SH 14\",\"link\":\"/UploadedFiles/Files/Form%20SH-14%20-%20Cancellation%20or%20Variation%20from%20Nomination.pdf\",\"description\":\"Cancellation / Variation from Nomination\"}],\"warningText\":\"If you fail to updates the above mentions details, in terms of aforesaid circular, your shares shall be frozen from October 01, 2023. Frozen folios shall be referred by the RTA / listed Company to the administering authority under the Benami Transactions (Prohibitions) Act, 19